@ Factorial Example Code in Kindred

func factorial(n: int): int
    case (n > 1) of:
        true => return n * factorial(n-1)
        false => return 1
    return -1 @ kind of disgusting but require a return in outer-scope of function (not nested)

func main:int():
    int n = read()
    print(factorial n)
    return 1